          <p
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed"
          >
            Crafting innovative solutions at the intersection of
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 dark:from-blue-400 dark:to-indigo-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Code</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mx-2">√ó</span>
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 dark:from-indigo-400 dark:to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Design</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mx-2">√ó</span>
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 dark:from-purple-400 dark:to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Innovation</span>
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap mb-8">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/bachboy0"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 text-white hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/50 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-95 overflow-hidden"
            >
              <span class="relative z-10">üêô My GitHub</span>
              <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></span>
            </a>
            <a
